(36, '2015-06-08 00:03:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 35003, 'new', 'Aurora-Oak Ridges-Richmond Hill', 'Ontario', '', 'Aurora-Oak Ridges-Richmond Hill is a new riding carved out of parts of Oak Ridges-Markham, Newmarket-Aurora and Richmond Hill.  Costas Menegakis, the Conservative incumbent for Richmond Hill, is running for re-election in this riding.  Leona Alleslev is running for the Liberals, and the other parties have not yet chosen candidates.', '', '', '', 20221, 10941, 6263, 1363, 0, 471, 9280, 13958, 39259, 18567, 47, 'Tory', 9280, 39259, 23.6379),
