(52, '2015-06-02 20:16:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 35019, 'redistricted', 'Don Valley East', 'Ontario', 'This is a riding that the Liberals have a good chance of taking back.', 'The new riding of Don Valley East is composed of the southern half of the old riding of Don Valley East, as well as a new area west of Bayview, plus Flemingdon Park.  This will be a wide open race, since the incumbent has chosen to run in Don Valley North.  With the addition of the new areas the Liberals, represented by former M.P. Yasmin Ratansi, should have a very good chance of beating the Conservatives, represented by Maureen Charquail.  However, this race may well be very close.', '', '', '', 12794, 13503, 7694, 994, 0, 187, -709, 5100, 35172, 22191, 63, 'Lib', 709, 35172, 2.01581),
(53, '2015-06-08 00:05:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 35020, 'new', 'Don Valley North', 'Ontario', 'There is a chance of defeating the Conservative in this riding.', 'Don Valley North is a new riding composed of the eastern part of Willowdale and the northern part of Don Valley East, north of the 401, which leaned more Conservative than the Southern part of Don Valley East. Joe Daniel, the Conservative incumbent for Don Valley East, is running for re-election in Don Valley North, the northern part of his current riding.  Based on previous voting patterns he will face a strong challenge from Liberal Geng Tang.  Akil Sadikali is running for the NDP.', '', '', '', 15801, 14625, 8129, 516, 0, 142, 1176, 7672, 39213, 23270, 59, 'Tory', 1176, 39213, 2.99901),
(54, '2015-06-04 18:04:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 35021, 'redistricted', 'Don Valley West', 'Ontario', 'This is a riding that the Liberals have a good chance of taking back.  ', 'Don Valley West is smaller than it was last election: a large section east of the Don Valley Parkway, which includes Flemingdon Park, is now in Don Valley East, and has been replaced by an area of Mount Pleasant East that used to be in the riding of St. Paul’s.  This riding was a very narrow win for Conservative John Carmichael in 2011; some robocalling may have played a part in that. Carmichael''s term has been unremarkable except for some <a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2015/06/03/john-carmichael-israel-ndp-nuclear-weapons-dewar_n_7506010.html">bizarre accusastions of anti-semitism.</a>  The riding’s former MP, Liberal Rob Oliphant, a Minister in the United Church, hopes to take the riding again in what may be a very close race', '', '', '', 19893, 18805, 4871, 1616, 0, 140, 1088, 15022, 45325, 25292, 56, 'Tory', 1088, 45325, 2.40044),
