(147, '2015-06-03 21:14:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 35114, 'redistricted', 'Whitby', 'Ontario', 'It will be a challenge to take this riding from the Conservatives.', 'The riding of Whitby is geographically smaller than the old riding of Whitby-Oshawa that elected Jim Flaherty and later Conservative Pat Perkins in the by-election after Flaherty''s death.  The riding has voted Conservative in all the elections in the last decade.  Pat Perkins will be running for re-election, challenged once again by Celina Caesar-Chavannes for the Liberals and Craig Cameron for the Green Party; the NDP have not yet announced a candidate.', '', '', '', 31034, 7644, 11297, 2628, 0, 168, 23390, 19737, 52771, 21569, 41, 'Tory', 19737, 52771, 37.4012),
(148, '2015-06-02 21:39:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 35115, 'redistricted', 'Willowdale', 'Ontario', 'Getting out the vote is key to taking back this riding.', 'The riding of Willowdale is composed of half of the old riding of Willowdale, West of Bayview, and a small part of the old riding of York Centre.   The riding is held by Conservative Chungsen Leung, who won by a very narrow margin in 2011.  This time Leung is being challenged by Liberal Ali Ehsassi.  Expect a very close race.  There is a campaign underway by LeadNow to inform people and encourage them to vote against the Conservative.  The voter turnout in 2011 was low; getting new Canadians to vote against the Conservatives could be the key to taking back this riding.', '', '', '', 16168, 15280, 7383, 152, 0, 0, 888, 8785, 38983, 22815, 59, 'Tory', 888, 38983, 2.27792),
