(152, '2015-06-04 21:31:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 35119, 'redistricted', 'York-Simcoe', 'Ontario', '', 'Voters in York-Simcoe are represented by Conservative Peter Van Loan, best known for <a href="http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2012/12/06/nearbrawl_erupts_in_commons_between_tory_peter_van_loan_and_ndps_nathan_cullen.html"> starting brawls with the opposition</a> and <a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2015/02/16/conservative-mailings_n_6694938.html"> sending out partisan mailings</a> on the taxpayer''s dime.  Shaun Tanaka is running for the Liberals.', '', '', '', 24624, 4385, 7187, 2073, 0, 408, 20239, 17437, 37700, 12668, 34, 'Tory', 17437, 37700, 46.252),
