(159, '2015-06-01 21:24:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 46005, 'redistricted', 'Elmwood-Transcona', 'Manitoba', 'Strategic voting needed in this riding.', 'Last election the NDP lost this riding by 300 votes.  Redistribution favours the Conservatives noticeably in Elmwood-Transcoma; a Conservative-leaning area of Kildonan-St. Paul was added to the riding to boost Conservative Incumbent Lawrence Toet''s margin from razor-thin to just very thin.  He is being challenged by Liberal Andrea Richardson-Lipon and New Democrat Daniel Blaikie.  This riding is one to watch, as a few voters lending their votes to the opposition candidate with the best chance of winning could prevent another conservative from returning to Parliament Hill.', '', '', '', 16086, 1779, 15364, 1053, 0, 7, 14307, 722, 34289, 18196, 53, 'Tory', 722, 34289, 2.10563),
