(408, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:13', '2015-06-28 23:47:13', 'NDP incumbent Carol Hughes is seeking a third term this year.  Liberal Heather Wilson is challenging her for the seat. </br>Député Carol Hughes souhaite être réélu pour le NPD.  Heather Wilson est la candidate Libérale.', 'Algoma-Manitoulin-Kapuskasing', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35002', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:13', '2015-06-28 23:47:13', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35002/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
(409, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:13', '2015-06-28 23:47:13', 'Aurora-Oak Ridges-Richmond Hill is a new riding carved out of parts of Oak Ridges-Markham, Newmarket-Aurora and Richmond Hill.  Costas Menegakis, the Conservative incumbent for Richmond Hill, is running for re-election in this riding.  Leona Alleslev is running for the Liberals, and the other parties have not yet chosen candidates.', 'Aurora-Oak Ridges-Richmond Hill', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35003', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:13', '2015-06-28 23:47:13', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35003/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
(410, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:13', '2015-06-28 23:47:13', 'Barrie-Innisfil is a new riding composed of parts of the old riding of Barrie and a small area of York-Simcoe.  There is no incumbent running in Barrie-Innisfil.  Myrna Clark is running for the NDP, Colin Wilson for the Liberals and Bonnie North for the Green Party.  The Conservatives have not yet announced a candidate.', 'Barrie-Innisfil', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35004', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:13', '2015-06-28 23:47:13', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35004/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
