(418, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:13', '2015-06-28 23:47:13', 'The new riding of Brampton West is composed of the area north of Queen Street of the old Brampton West riding.   The incumbent Conservative is running in the new riding of Brampton South.  With this new distribution the Liberals, represented by Kamalpreet Krera, have a much better chance of catching up with the Conservatives, who have not yet picked a candidate.  Adaoma Patterson is running for the NDP.', 'Brampton West', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35012', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:13', '2015-06-28 23:47:13', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35012/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
