(423, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:13', '2015-06-28 23:47:13', 'The riding of Chatham-Kent-Essex has had its boundaries altered slightly and its name changed to Chatham-Kent-Leamington.  If previous voting patterns hold incumbent Dave Van Kesteren will probably retain his seat.  His main challenger is Tony Walsh for the NDP, as well as Katie Omstead for the Liberals.', 'Chatham-Kent-Leamington', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35017', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:13', '2015-06-28 23:47:13', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35017/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
