(450, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:14', '2015-06-28 23:47:14', 'The northern Conservative-leaning portion of the riding has been redistributed to Lanark-Frontenac, so former mayor Mark Gerretsen, running for the Liberals, will have a better chance of winning this than he would have before distribution.  Candidates for the NDP (Daniel Beals) and the Green Party (Nathan Townend) will challenge him, along with Andy Brooke for the Conservatives. As the Conservatives came a close second last time, non-conservatives will have to keep an eye on developments to see if they need to ward off a Conservative threat.', 'Kingston and the Islands', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35044', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:14', '2015-06-28 23:47:14', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35044/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
