(496, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:15', '2015-06-28 23:47:15', 'The boundaries of Toronto St-Paul''s cover a slightly smaller geographical area than the riding of St. Paul''s did, since a small area east of Bayview was redistributed to Don Valley West.  Liberal incumbent Carolyn Bennett, who has represented the riding since 1997, is running for re-election.  Marnie MacDougall is running for the Conservatives; the other parties have not yet selected their candidates.', 'Toronto-St. Paul''s', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35090', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:15', '2015-06-28 23:47:15', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35090/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
