(499, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:15', '2015-06-28 23:47:15', 'The graph on this page shows the results of the by-election of 2014, when the riding gave the Liberals, represented by Arnold Chan, a much wider victory than they had for his predecessor Jim Karygiannis in the 2011 General election. Chan is running for re-election, challenged by Bin Chang for the Conservatives.  So far the other parties have not nominated candidates. ', 'Scarborough-Agincourt', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35093', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:15', '2015-06-28 23:47:15', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35093/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
(500, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:15', '2015-06-28 23:47:15', 'Last election this was a three-way race narrowly won by Conservative Roxanne James.   She is running for re-election against Liberal challenger Salmer Zahid and Alex Wilson for the NDP, who will both battle hard for the riding.  Historically the riding has voted for all three parties.  Non-Conservative voters will need to keep their ears to the ground to decide whether to vote Liberal or NDP to ensure a Conservative defeat - national trends of one party rising in popularity are not always reflected in the riding.  Last election the voter turnout was below the national average, so getting out the non-Conservative vote will be key in what may be a close race.\r\n', 'Scarborough Centre', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35094', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:15', '2015-06-28 23:47:15', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35094/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
(501, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:15', '2015-06-28 23:47:15', 'Scarborough-Guildwood is slightly smaller now, as parts of it have been redistributed to other ridings.  The riding is held by Liberal John McKay, who is running for re-election, but based on voting patterns from previous elections, expect a close race between McKay and Conservative Kazimierz Konkel.   In previous elections the voter turnout in this riding has been well below the average for Canada.', 'Scarborough-Guildwood', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35095', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:15', '2015-06-28 23:47:15', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35095/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
