(504, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:15', '2015-06-28 23:47:15', 'Most voters in Scarborough Southwest, held by NDP Dan Harris, are in the same riding as in 2011, with the exception of a few north of Eglinton and some east of Bellamy.  Last time the riding was a three-way race with a voter turnout that was lower than average.  NDP incumbent Dan Harris is running for re-election against challengers that have not yet been nominated.  Bill Blair is a high-profile candidate seeking the Liberal nomination.', 'Scarborough Southwest', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35098', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:15', '2015-06-28 23:47:15', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35098/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
