(520, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:16', '2015-06-28 23:47:16', 'The riding of Whitby is geographically smaller than the old riding of Whitby-Oshawa that elected Jim Flaherty and later Conservative Pat Perkins in the by-election after Flaherty''s death.  The riding has voted Conservative in all the elections in the last decade.  Pat Perkins will be running for re-election, challenged once again by Celina Caesar-Chavannes for the Liberals and Craig Cameron for the Green Party; the NDP have not yet announced a candidate.', 'Whitby', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35114', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:16', '2015-06-28 23:47:16', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35114/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
(521, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:16', '2015-06-28 23:47:16', 'The riding of Willowdale is composed of half of the old riding of Willowdale, West of Bayview, and a small part of the old riding of York Centre.   The riding is held by Conservative Chungsen Leung, who won by a very narrow margin in 2011.  This time Leung is being challenged by Liberal Ali Ehsassi.  Expect a very close race.  There is a campaign underway by LeadNow to inform people and encourage them to vote against the Conservative.  The voter turnout in 2011 was low; getting new Canadians to vote against the Conservatives could be the key to taking back this riding.', 'Willowdale', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35115', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:16', '2015-06-28 23:47:16', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35115/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
