(525, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:16', '2015-06-28 23:47:16', 'Voters in York-Simcoe are represented by Conservative Peter Van Loan, best known for <a href="http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2012/12/06/nearbrawl_erupts_in_commons_between_tory_peter_van_loan_and_ndps_nathan_cullen.html"> starting brawls with the opposition</a> and <a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2015/02/16/conservative-mailings_n_6694938.html"> sending out partisan mailings</a> on the taxpayer''s dime.  Shaun Tanaka is running for the Liberals.', 'York-Simcoe', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '35119', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:16', '2015-06-28 23:47:16', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/35119/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
