(529, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:16', '2015-06-28 23:47:16', 'After losing the use of his limbs in a car accident, Stephen Fletcher was told he would spend the rest of his life in an institution.  He jokes that the doctors never suspected that the institution would be Parliament.  He is running for his fifth term as a Conservative, challenged by Liberal Doug Eyolfson, who happens to be an emergency room doctor.  The NDP are seeking someone equally heroic to join them.', 'Charleswood-St. James-Assiniboia-Headingley', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '46002', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:16', '2015-06-28 23:47:16', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/46002/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
