(544, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:17', '2015-06-28 23:47:17', 'The Conservatives won here by an extremely narrow margin in 2011.  Incumbent Rob Clarke is running for re-election, challenged by two candidates: Joseph Lawrence, who lost narrowly in 2011 as a candidate for the NDP, but is running for the Liberals in 2015, as well as Georgina Jolibois, Mayor of La Loche, who is running for the NDP.  It is vital in this riding for people determined to change the government that they choose one of the two to unite behind.', 'Desnethé–Missinippi–Churchill River', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '47003', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:17', '2015-06-28 23:47:17', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/47003/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
