(585, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:18', '2015-06-28 23:47:18', 'The new riding of Red Deer-Lacombe is a combination of the old ridings of Wetaskiwin and Red Deer.  Blaine Calkins, the Conservative incumbent for Wetaskiwin, is running for re-election in this riding.  He is noted for saying that Liberal Justin Trudeau will <a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2014/02/10/blaine-calkins-trudeau-guns-video_n_4762981.html"> have to pry his gun from his cold, dead hands</a> and for thinking of <a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/dave-coles/bill-c-525-canadian-unions_b_3403630.html"> ingenious ways </a> to thwart unions.  Clergyman Jeffrey Rock will contest the seat for the Liberals.', 'Red Deer-Lacombe', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '48030', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:18', '2015-06-28 23:47:18', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/48030/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
(586, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:18', '2015-06-28 23:47:18', 'The change in name for this riding reflects its more rural nature, as the riding has been shifted Westward and includes less of Edmonton.  Voters here gave Brent Rathgeber a resounding victory when he ran as a Conservative.   In the last two years, since leaving the Conservative caucus, he has acted as a true Independent and has endeavoured to take a <a href="http://brentrathgeber.ca/">conscientious stance on each issue</a> as it comes up.  He is running for re-election as an Independent.  Voters who wish to defeat the Conservative government could consider voting for him, since he would not add to the seat count of their party.  Michael Cooper is running for the Conservatives, and the other parties have not yet chosen candidates.', 'St. Albert-Edmonton', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '48031', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:18', '2015-06-28 23:47:18', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/48031/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
(587, 0, '2015-06-28 19:47:18', '2015-06-28 23:47:18', 'This renamed riding is composed mainly of the old riding of Edmonton--Sherwood Park along with a few voters from Vegreville--Wainwright.  ', 'Sherwood Park-Fort Saskatchewan', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '48032', '', '', '2015-06-28 19:47:18', '2015-06-28 23:47:18', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/48032/', 0, 'riding', '', 0),
