(721, 1, '2015-06-30 11:53:12', '2015-06-30 15:53:12', 'The purpose of this site is to gather information to enable voters to decide which candidate in their riding has the best chance of defeating the Conservative who is running.\r\n\r\nAt this point (early July) national polls are showing a huge decrease in support for the Conservatives and an upsurge in support for the NDP.  National polls, even provincial polls, do a very poor job of predicting the race in a given riding.  Adjacent ridings will have local factors that have them voting very different ways.\r\n\r\nThe information on your riding will be gathered by you and others like you, people who believe that we need a government that better reflects our values.  Your input will help others make their decisions.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About This Site', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'about-this-site', '', '', '2015-07-08 13:35:38', '2015-07-08 17:35:38', '', 0, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/?page_id=721', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(722, 1, '2015-06-30 11:51:44', '2015-06-30 15:51:44', 'The purpose of this site is to gather information to enable voters to decide which candidate in their riding has the best chance of defeating the Conservative who is running.\r\n\r\nAt this point polls are showing a huge decrease in support for the Conservatives and an upsurge in support for the NDP.\r\n\r\nNational polls do a very poor job of predicting the race in a given riding.  Adjacent ridings will have local factors that have them voting very different ways.\r\n\r\nIf your priority is to unseat the Harper Conservatives, you will need to know who to vote for in your riding.  We hope that you will use this site as a place to exchange information and decide who has the best chance locally.\r\n\r\nYou will need data that is more precise than national polls to know whether you will be able to vote for your party of choice or must consider voting for another to defeat a Conservative in a close race.', 'About This Site', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '721-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-30 11:51:44', '2015-06-30 15:51:44', '', 721, 'http://defeatharper.ca/wordpress/721-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
